266
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:37,950
- One, two, three.
- One, two, three.

267
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:40,180
- Here we go.
- Let's go.

268
00:19:40,250 --> 00:19:42,650
Please leave them there.
Leave them there.

269
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:44,250
Leave them there.

270
00:19:44,619 --> 00:19:46,619
- Just...
- One, two...

271
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:52,460
(100-year-old Finnish birch)

272
00:20:17,119 --> 00:20:20,259
