closer to his employees?

273
00:20:20,759 --> 00:20:23,660
He even reached out first.

274
00:20:24,089 --> 00:20:28,170
Is he really the psychopath
who wanted no one near his door?

275
00:20:31,799 --> 00:20:34,569
I can never fire her in person.

276
00:20:34,910 --> 00:20:37,009
Right, I should e-mail her.

277
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:48,150
Dear Ms. Chae Ro Woon...

278
00:20:48,190 --> 00:20:49,349
(Dear Ms. Chae Ro Woon)

279
00:20:51,190 --> 00:20:52,289
Unfortunately...

280
00:20:52,319 --> 00:20:54,890
No. Regrettably...

281
00:20:56,690 --> 00:20:59,329
I must say... I'm afraid...

282
00:20:59,799 --> 00:21:01,259
Sadly...

283
00:21:01,529 --> 00:21:04,670
The company and you seem to
have differing...

284
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:17,579
Dear Ms. Chae Ro Woon...

285
00:21:25,319 --> 00:21:26,660
Mr. Eun.

286
00:21:35,369 --> 00:21:36,369
What is it?

287
00:21:36,869 --> 00:21:38,569
I'm sorry to interrupt.

288
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:41,039
We have some coffee for you.

289
00:21:43,740 --> 00:21:47,210
Since you didn't give us
any instructions, we prepared...

290
00:21:47,779 --> 00:21:50,380
