291
00:21:51,779 --> 00:21:54,180
Could you be with us for a moment?

292
00:21:56,490 --> 00:21:59,490
We'll take this cake.

293
00:21:59,559 --> 00:22:01,630
- Okay.
- We'll have...

294
00:22:02,430 --> 00:22:04,460
three Americanos, two lattes,

295
00:22:04,490 --> 00:22:05,559
and...

296
00:22:07,829 --> 00:22:09,430
What should we get for him?

297
00:22:11,269 --> 00:22:12,240
I'm not sure.

298
00:22:12,269 --> 00:22:13,940
Don't you know
what kind of coffee he drinks?

299
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,569
Mr. Eun never...

300
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:18,109
asked me for coffee.

301
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:22,680
Now that I think of it, he was
probably trying to be considerate.

302
00:22:23,079 --> 00:22:25,420
When someone asks you for coffee,

303
00:22:25,549 --> 00:22:27,380
it can sometimes
make you feel small.

304
00:22:27,450 --> 00:22:30,849
He has surprisingly good manners.

305
00:22:30,890 --> 00:22:32,519
Have you made up your mind?

306
00:22:34,019 --> 00:22:36,390
I don't think he'll like
something sweet.

307
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:40,329
I'd go for...

308
00:22:40,859 --> 00:22:42,569
three espresso shots.

309
00:22:43,569 --> 00:22:44,700
