Among all of us, you're probably...

333
00:23:49,769 --> 00:23:52,640
the one who's been saying
"Mr. Eun" most often.

334
00:23:52,940 --> 00:23:53,940
Me?

335
00:23:53,970 --> 00:23:56,039
Give it a try, Gyo Ri.

336
00:23:56,509 --> 00:23:59,140
- Yes, do it.
- Be confident.

337
00:24:05,980 --> 00:24:07,079
Hwan Gi.

338
00:24:18,660 --> 00:24:20,630
My gosh, I'm so sorry.

339
00:24:26,869 --> 00:24:28,940
Oh, no. He must be mad at me.

340
00:24:30,210 --> 00:24:32,539
See? I said I didn't want to do it.

341
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,809
What should I do now?

342
00:24:34,849 --> 00:24:36,210
He has such a foul temper.

343
00:24:57,029 --> 00:25:01,000
I do always wear black, but it does
not mean I like my coffee black.

344
00:25:01,839 --> 00:25:06,210
I only drink caramel macchiato,
caffe mocha with whipped cream,

345
00:25:06,579 --> 00:25:09,910
or coffee with a ton of sugar and
cream. Should I tell them my taste?

346
00:25:10,650 --> 00:25:14,019
No, no. They probably put a lot
of thought and consideration...

347
00:25:14,049 --> 00:25:16,950
into figuring out what kind of
coffee I'd like. It'd be too rude.

348
00:25:16,990 --> 00:25:18,220
(Politeness)

349
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:21,059
Shall I dump this into the sink
when no one is looking?

350
00:25:21,589 --> 00:25:23,660
They went all the way there
and got this for me. I shouldn't.

351
00:25:24,660 --> 00:25:26,400
Shall I put some sugar in it?

352
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:29,900
Even a whole jar of sugar
won't be enough.

353
00:25:30,269 --> 00:25:32,240
I might end up with diabetes, then.

354
00:25:33,140 --> 00:25:37,809
But drinking this bitter coffee as
it is will damage my stomach lining.

355
00:25:41,339 --> 00:25:42,750
How about I add some water?

356
00:25:45,579 --> 00:25:46,950
(Water and coffee)

357
00:25:49,049 --> 00:25:50,150
Yes, that's it.

358
00:25:50,319 --> 00:25:53,160
I should pour out a little bit
and add water to dilute it.

359
00:25:56,759 --> 00:25:58,130
Mr. Eun.

360
00:26:05,299 --> 00:26:07,269
Is that the coffee I got for you...

361
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:09,640
How can you do this
right in front of her?

362
00:26:10,539 --> 00:26:12,940
I get that she called you
by your name, but this is too cruel.

363
00:26:12,980 --> 00:26:14,039
Don't.

364
00:26:14,910 --> 00:26:16,809
I apologize, Mr. Eun.

365
00:26:17,549 --> 00:26:20,819
I got carried away and said
your name without even realizing it.

366
00:26:21,619 --> 00:26:23,150
I'm sorry for crossing the line.

367
00:26:29,859 --> 00:26:32,859
Everyone's waiting for you.
Please come and cut the cake.

368
00:26:36,069 --> 00:26:37,730
Where's the knife?

369
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,539
Oh, that cabinet is...

370
