371
00:26:55,950 --> 00:26:57,150
My personal collection.

372
00:26:57,750 --> 00:26:58,960
May I...

373
00:27:00,119 --> 00:27:02,329
borrow just one knife?

374
00:27:04,059 --> 00:27:05,460
I mean, you have so many.

375
00:27:11,599 --> 00:27:13,240
That's the sashimi knife
I sharpened this morning!

376
00:27:18,009 --> 00:27:19,279
This will be perfect...

377
00:27:19,380 --> 00:27:21,339
- for cutting cake.
- Be careful!

378
00:27:25,519 --> 00:27:27,079
- What's going on?
- What happened?

379
00:27:34,759 --> 00:27:36,789
Please do not touch
my personal collection.

380
00:28:00,079 --> 00:28:02,450
Let me see. Are you all right?
You didn't get hurt, did you?

381
00:28:02,549 --> 00:28:07,190
I knew it. He's showing his true
colors. He's not Silent Monster.

382
00:28:08,220 --> 00:28:10,190
Shouldn't he be called
Psychopath Monster?

383
00:28:46,460 --> 00:28:49,000
Even cars can shout like this.

384
00:28:50,470 --> 00:28:53,039
Why am I like this, seriously?

385
00:28:57,809 --> 00:29:00,240
Hey, Ms. Chae. Come on in.

386
00:29:02,150 --> 00:29:04,849
Your office door is always open...

387
00:29:05,279 --> 00:29:06,750
unlike someone else's office.

388
00:29:07,220 --> 00:29:08,789
I don't like feeling boxed in.

389
00:29:09,289 --> 00:29:13,160
