401
00:32:08,630 --> 00:32:10,000
I can't wear that just on its own.

402
00:32:11,029 --> 00:32:12,700
Can you try to find the same design?

403
00:32:13,799 --> 00:32:16,170
Yes. I'm sorry, Ro Woon.

404
00:32:17,609 --> 00:32:20,210
I don't think I can make it today.

405
00:32:21,380 --> 00:32:23,480
I'm sorry for missing your musical.
Best of luck with it.

406
00:32:23,509 --> 00:32:25,450
I don't need flowers.
I want you here.

407
00:32:36,329 --> 00:32:38,630
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

408
00:32:59,650 --> 00:33:01,819
Hello? This is the flower
delivery service, right?

409
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:24,309
So are you asking
what kind of person Hwan Gi is?

410
00:33:25,269 --> 00:33:28,009
You said that you're his only
friend and confidant.

411
00:33:29,150 --> 00:33:31,109
Don't believe those scary,
bizarre rumors about him.

412
00:33:31,509 --> 00:33:35,079
The courier guy with sad eyes
is closer to who he really is.

413
00:33:36,650 --> 00:33:38,420
Will you believe me if I say that?

414
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:41,690
