no one would believe it.

417
00:33:49,869 --> 00:33:53,970
That's why everyone was reluctant
to join Silent Monster under him.

418
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:55,869
Since you volunteered to join,

419
00:33:56,309 --> 00:33:58,009
we have high expectations of you.

420
00:33:58,240 --> 00:34:01,480
Gosh, I don't know anything.

421
00:34:02,750 --> 00:34:04,410
Just think of it lightly.

422
00:34:04,849 --> 00:34:07,720
People are what our company
is trying to sell.

423
00:34:09,289 --> 00:34:11,190
Do you mean just sugarcoat it?

424
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:16,489
The cover of a book
isn't everything.

425
00:34:17,090 --> 00:34:18,900
However, if you want to solve
a problem fast,

426
00:34:18,929 --> 00:34:20,360
sugarcoating is necessary.

427
00:34:21,159 --> 00:34:24,000
