476
00:37:02,489 --> 00:37:05,429
- My goodness, that's my phone.
- Hello? Where are you?

477
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:22,079
What do you need to tell me?

478
00:37:22,179 --> 00:37:23,849
Am I supposed to stand here all day?

479
00:37:24,550 --> 00:37:27,619
Where did you go off to
during office hours?

480
00:37:27,719 --> 00:37:30,449
I was working.
I had a meeting with a client.

481
00:37:31,289 --> 00:37:32,250
Is that true?

482
00:37:32,289 --> 00:37:34,719
Ask Mr. Kang
if you don't believe me.

483
00:37:34,989 --> 00:37:36,230
I met Actor Hwang.

484
00:37:36,530 --> 00:37:39,000
You know, the one that's
involved in a scandal?

485
00:37:39,329 --> 00:37:41,599
He was hiding at a hotel
from the press.

486
00:37:41,630 --> 00:37:42,869
All right, get back to work.

487
00:37:43,730 --> 00:37:44,730
Pardon?

488
00:37:45,639 --> 00:37:47,170
That's it?

489
00:37:49,610 --> 00:37:51,840
I ran all the way here
because you said it was urgent.

490
00:37:54,579 --> 00:37:55,579
