491
00:38:00,219 --> 00:38:01,679
The cake?

492
00:38:02,179 --> 00:38:05,349
Did you call me and make a fuss...

493
00:38:06,320 --> 00:38:07,389
because of that?

494
00:38:07,989 --> 00:38:08,989
You're dismissed.

495
00:38:14,130 --> 00:38:17,199
Does he not have hands and feet?

496
00:38:17,699 --> 00:38:19,639
He could have done it himself.

497
00:38:19,869 --> 00:38:22,809
Why did he rush me to clean up
leftover cake?

498
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:26,639
Gosh. You jerk.

499
00:38:26,710 --> 00:38:28,440
You'll pay for this!

500
00:38:31,550 --> 00:38:32,619
I'm so mad.

501
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:34,579
(New York Barbershop)

502
00:38:38,650 --> 00:38:40,559
- Did you eat?
- Yes.

503
00:38:40,719 --> 00:38:41,760
Hey.

504
00:38:42,789 --> 00:38:44,190
I said I ate.

505
00:38:59,340 --> 00:39:00,539
Mr. Smith?

506
00:39:06,050 --> 00:39:07,719
(New York Barbershop)

507
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:47,860
(I'll wait for your return
to the stage.)

508
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:50,090
I'll wait for your return
to the stage.

509
00:39:53,030 --> 00:39:55,559
What should I do, Mr. Smith?

510
00:39:57,800 --> 00:39:58,800
I...

511
00:40:02,039 --> 00:40:04,309
still have something I must do.

512
00:40:20,789 --> 00:40:21,789
Boss.

513
00:40:23,659 --> 00:40:25,659
You're not here, right?

514
00:40:47,019 --> 00:40:48,050
What are you doing?

515
00:41:03,070 --> 00:41:04,130
I...

516
00:41:06,039 --> 00:41:08,699
I have a meeting with a client.

517
00:41:09,869 --> 00:41:10,909
At this hour?

518
00:41:11,409 --> 00:41:12,539
It was someone...

519
00:41:13,010 --> 00:41:15,739
It's someone that can't be seen
by the public.

520
00:41:40,469 --> 00:41:44,469
Mr. Kang told me I should
start working on the PI Project.

521
00:41:44,570 --> 00:41:46,940
In order to PR something,

