00:59:25,670 --> 00:59:27,099
Mr. Kang.

784
00:59:28,840 --> 00:59:31,340
I'm not sure why you chose
to give up your dream,

785
00:59:31,369 --> 00:59:32,409
but I'm grateful.

786
00:59:33,679 --> 00:59:34,809
For what?

787
00:59:36,110 --> 00:59:39,909
Thanks to that decision, I got an
employee with a bright future ahead.

788
00:59:41,380 --> 00:59:44,820
You trust anyone who has eyes
that look trustworthy to you.

789
00:59:45,250 --> 00:59:47,989
When everyone else was saying
that he's a thief,

790
00:59:48,119 --> 00:59:49,989
you kept trusting him.

791
00:59:50,829 --> 00:59:53,630
That courier guy didn't turn out
to be whom you thought he was,

792
00:59:53,800 --> 00:59:56,130
but you turned around
only to trust someone else again.

793
00:59:57,130 --> 00:59:58,900
When everyone else was
saying it's adultery,

794
00:59:58,929 --> 01:00:00,699
you trusted his claim...

795
01:00:02,099 --> 01:00:04,510
and ended up getting slapped
in the face.

796
01:00:06,909 --> 01:00:10,880
I know that you'll become the best
PR specialist of Korea.

797
01:00:12,280 --> 01:00:13,309
I believe in you.

798
01:00:16,519 --> 01:00:20,250
You shouldn't trust people
that easily.

799
01:00:20,920 --> 01:00:23,090
You could be backstabbed, slapped,

800
01:00:23,860 --> 01:00:25,860
or get punched right in the eye.

801
01:00:26,690 --> 01:00:27,860
Let's go to the gathering.

802
01:00:30,030 --> 01:00:31,829
You really shouldn't.

803
01:00:32,570 --> 01:00:36,570
I'm here for revenge.
You shouldn't trust me like this.

804
01:01:00,030 --> 01:01:01,059
Please...

805
01:01:03,000 --> 01:01:04,170
join us for the gathering.

806
01:01:04,230 --> 01:01:05,300
Gathering?

807
01:01:05,329 --> 01:01:07,440
Mr. Kang is taking us out
for barbecue.

808
01:01:07,469 --> 01:01:09,269
We didn't throw a proper
launching ceremony today.

809
01:01:10,469 --> 01:01:13,170
I... I need some time.

810
01:01:13,210 --> 01:01:15,110
Are you busy with something?

811
01:01:29,420 --> 01:01:30,590
By any chance,

812
01:01:31,329 --> 01:01:34,230
is there a problem
with our kimchi refrigerator?

813
01:01:44,840 --> 01:01:45,840
Goodness.

814
01:01:48,940 --> 01:01:49,940
Could you...

815
01:01:51,150 --> 01:01:52,409
give me a minute?

816
01:02:00,119 --> 01:02:01,260
Let's just go.

817
01:02:01,420 --> 01:02:03,360
He asked us to wait for him.

818
01:02:03,389 --> 01:02:05,130
It's our team dinner, you know.

819
01:02:05,159 --> 01:02:07,960
He won't come. I mean, he doesn't
even attend our meetings.

820
01:02:15,000 --> 01:02:16,039
Let's go.

821
01:02:19,139 --> 01:02:20,309
But I must say,

822
01:02:20,679 --> 01:02:24,150
I'm so happy that we have such
a caring boss like you, Mr. Kang.

823
01:02:56,440 --> 01:02:58,880
Did you stop me from opening it
to age the fish properly?

824
01:02:59,679 --> 01:03:01,019
To keep the temperature perfect?

825
01:03:04,420 --> 01:03:06,449
Would you like
to have some of this with me?

826
01:03:07,760 --> 01:03:09,059
I can't finish it all by myself.

827
01:03:34,380 --> 01:03:36,349
Let's go eat barbecue.
I'm so excited.

828
01:03:36,380 --> 01:03:37,650
I need to eat to refuel myself.

829
01:03:37,690 --> 01:03:38,989
- Will you be all right?
- I'm fine.

830
01:03:39,019 --> 01:03:41,989
You need to exercise.
Start working out, will you?

831
01:03:42,019 --> 01:03:44,059
- Why are you hitting me?
- You embarrass me.

832
01:03:44,090 --> 01:03:46,489
- Where are you taking us?
- Eat something nourishing today.

833
01:03:51,469 --> 01:03:53,329
Dad, I'm here.

834
01:03:55,039 --> 01:03:56,699
It's almost time for the flight.

835
01:03:59,610 --> 01:04:00,980
Okay.

836
01:04:01,210 --> 01:04:03,079
I'm hungry. Hurry up.

837
01:04:03,179 --> 01:04:04,309
(Actor Hwang Faces Penalty
for Breach of Contract)

838
01:04:06,750 --> 01:04:08,119
That woman...

839
01:04:11,150 --> 01:04:12,289
"Dad"?

840
01:04:19,389 --> 01:04:23,730
- It said "My daughter".
- That can't be.

841
01:04:23,900 --> 01:04:25,900
He only has a son.

842
01:04:27,900 --> 01:04:30,139
Ro Woon, what are you doing?

843
01:04:31,340 --> 01:04:33,139
Ro Woon, come on.

844
01:04:34,179 --> 01:04:37,010
I'll meet you guys there.
I left something at the office.

845
01:04:38,050 --> 01:04:39,610
We'll go ahead and order barbecue.

846
01:04:39,750 --> 01:04:41,719
Hey, come with us.

847
01:04:44,849 --> 01:04:46,190
Let's just go.

848
01:04:47,659 --> 01:04:49,989
I wish she could come with us.

849
01:05:17,590 --> 01:05:20,789
I don't care
about what people think,

850
01:05:21,420 --> 01:05:23,960
but the problem is her.

851
01:05:26,159 --> 01:05:27,829
She doesn't want it.

852
01:05:28,599 --> 01:05:30,929
It is a very private matter,
you know.

853
01:05:31,070 --> 01:05:34,900
She doesn't understand why
other people need to know about it.

854
01:05:36,269 --> 01:05:38,539
She says that she doesn't need
people's approval.

855
01:05:40,679 --> 01:05:43,440
Not everyone wants
to come out of the closet...

856
01:05:43,809 --> 01:05:45,980
just because he or she has chosen
to live outside the norm.

857
01:05:47,619 --> 01:05:49,119
Come out of the closet?

858
01:05:50,579 --> 01:05:52,690
Does that mean he has been
keeping silent...

859
01:05:53,889 --> 01:05:55,989
in order to protect his family?

860
01:06:01,159 --> 01:06:04,699
All right.
These are articles about Mr. Hwang.

861
01:06:04,929 --> 01:06:07,300
We might find some clues here.

862
01:06:07,340 --> 01:06:08,570
Please go through them.

863
01:06:09,070 --> 01:06:10,340
Pass them around.

864
01:06:11,670 --> 01:06:13,869
(Hwang Yeong Gyu Reveals
His Only Son for the First Time)

865
01:06:14,139 --> 01:06:17,139
(In-Depth Interview with the Perfect
Man, Hwang Yeong Gyu)

866
01:06:17,179 --> 01:06:19,949
(The Honest Actor is Also an Honest
Dad to His Only Son)

867
01:06:26,849 --> 01:06:27,960
(My daughter)

868
01:06:36,429 --> 01:06:40,300
Dad, I'm scared of people.

869
01:06:42,400 --> 01:06:44,239
I think everyone hates me.

870
01:06:53,050 --> 01:06:57,719
I'm going to keep you safe,
so don't worry about anything.

871
01:06:57,949 --> 01:06:59,920
- All right?
- The woman in the photo...

872
01:07:00,550 --> 01:07:02,019
was his son.

873
01:07:02,789 --> 01:07:05,289
- Don't worry, okay?
- He has chosen to live...

874
01:07:05,329 --> 01:07:07,559
a new life as a woman.

875
01:07:09,099 --> 01:07:12,869
He was in so many reality shows
and TV commercials because of me.

876
01:07:13,829 --> 01:07:17,269
He has been in the public eye
since he was very young.

877
01:07:19,139 --> 01:07:21,039
Even a veteran actor like me...

878
01:07:21,409 --> 01:07:24,409
is still not used to public exposure
to this date.

879
01:07:39,329 --> 01:07:40,860
I like that reaction.

880
01:07:41,599 --> 01:07:45,400
It's devoid of useless
consolation, pity, or curiosity.

881
01:07:46,300 --> 01:07:47,699
You're so nonchalant about it.

882
01:07:56,239 --> 01:07:57,510
Thanks.

883
01:08:01,980 --> 01:08:03,280
All right, then.

884
01:08:07,219 --> 01:08:09,489
I should go meet my son... No.

885
01:08:11,090 --> 01:08:12,889
I mean my daughter.

886
01:08:30,109 --> 01:08:32,350
That psychopath...

887
01:08:33,149 --> 01:08:34,949
Who is he, seriously?

888
01:09:31,539 --> 01:09:33,369
Can I ask you something?

889
01:09:37,439 --> 01:09:38,880
On the rooftop,

890
01:09:40,010 --> 01:09:43,050
you kept apologizing over and over.

891
01:09:44,920 --> 01:09:46,819
Whom was the apology for?

892
01:09:52,229 --> 01:09:56,229
If there's something
you'd like to say to me...

893
01:09:56,859 --> 01:09:58,130
Her.

894
01:09:59,430 --> 01:10:00,699
For whom?

895
01:10:01,800 --> 01:10:04,000
What are you so sorry for?

896
01:10:04,970 --> 01:10:06,539
I wanted to keep her safe...

897
01:10:07,609 --> 01:10:09,609
so that she doesn't get hurt.

898
01:10:11,010 --> 01:10:13,449
Tell me. Please?

899
01:10:14,779 --> 01:10:16,319
I'm sorry.

900
01:10:18,119 --> 01:10:21,189
There's someone else...

901
01:10:22,359 --> 01:10:24,119
I must protect.

902
01:11:52,310 --> 01:11:55,380
(My Shy Boss)

903
01:11:55,420 --> 01:11:56,920
They're together again.

904
01:11:57,520 --> 01:11:59,619
Where are they going together?

905
01:12:00,449 --> 01:12:01,520
You're getting on my nerves.

906
01:12:01,560 --> 01:12:03,060
I'm the one in charge
of Silent Monster.

907
01:12:03,090 --> 01:12:05,489
- I'll take care of my staff.
- How are you going to do that?

908
01:12:05,529 --> 01:12:07,560
Are you two arguing right now?

909
01:12:07,590 --> 01:12:09,500
Do you actually want to
protect your staff?

910
01:12:09,699 --> 01:12:10,960
Ro Woon.

911
01:12:11,000 --> 01:12:12,729
Or are you just trying
to protect your pride?

912
01:12:13,170 --> 01:12:16,100
I'm sorry. I'm heading out
to grab a drink with my staff.

913
01:12:16,470 --> 01:12:17,810
Which ones?

914
01:12:18,109 --> 01:12:20,310
- Good work, everyone.
- See you tomorrow.

915
01:12:20,340 --> 01:12:24,310
What does he do alone here
after all of us leave?

916
01:12:24,340 --> 01:12:26,850
He only wears black, too.
He's like a cockroach.

917
01:12:26,880 --> 01:12:29,649
When everyone is asleep
and he's alone,

918
01:12:29,680 --> 01:12:30,850
he dances.

919
01:12:32,789 --> 01:12:34,119
He dances?
